\title{Helper Scripts}
\p{This skill includes comprehensive Python scripts for BRENDA database queries:}

\subtree{
\title{scripts/brenda_queries.py}
\p{Provides high-level functions for enzyme data analysis:}

\p{\strong{Key Functions}:}

\ul{
\li{\code{\startverb parse_km_entry(entry)\stopverb}: Parse BRENDA Km data entries}
\li{\code{\startverb parse_reaction_entry(entry)\stopverb}: Parse reaction data entries}
